Text: A product of the corporate music machine from the 80s. Quite good in her day, and might have had a chance to make it if the record company execs hadn't had their grubby little paws shoved so hard up her back that she just did what she was told, when she was told.
Downloading, I'd go so far as to say this would be interesting, at least. Thanks .BONE.
One sick old pedophile, and one screwed up freak, plus a home movie camera, do not amount to a "documentary". That's the most ridiculous pile of crap I've ever seen.
